ce for your ticket?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/35.mp3","time_start":91.88,"time_end":94.55},{"position":36,"content":"I paid £23.70.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/36.mp3","time_start":94.6,"time_end":97.12},{"position":37,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/37.mp3","time_start":97.12,"time_end":97.84},{"position":38,"content":"Do you think that's good value for money?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/38.mp3","time_start":98.03,"time_end":100.0},{"position":39,"content":"Not really.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/39.mp3","time_start":100.0,"time_end":100.87},{"position":40,"content":"I think it's too much for a journey that only takes 45 minutes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/40.mp3","time_start":100.87,"time_end":104.56},{"position":41,"content":"Yes, that's one of the main complaints we get.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/41.mp3","time_start":104.56,"time_end":107.32},{"position":42,"content":"So, you didn't buy your ticket in advance?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/42.mp3","time_start":107.49,"time_end":110.29},{"position":43,"content":"No.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/43.mp3","time_start":110.29,"time_end":111.28},{"position":44,"content":"I know it's cheaper if you buy a week in advance 