.85,"time_end":137.07},{"position":53,"content":"There's always a queue for the machines and they're often out of order.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/53-2024-11-03-17-33-23.mp3","time_start":137.0,"time_end":140.33},{"position":54,"content":"Hmm... A lot of customers are saying the same thing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/54.mp3","time_start":140.33,"time_end":143.04},{"position":55,"content":"So to answer your question... I got an e-ticket online.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/55.mp3","time_start":143.17,"time_end":148.27},{"position":56,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/56.mp3","time_start":148.92,"time_end":149.93},{"position":57,"content":"Thank you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/57.mp3","time_start":149.99,"time_end":151.13},{"position":58,"content":"Now I'd like to ask you about your satisfaction with your journey.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/58.mp3","time_start":151.13,"time_end":155.12},{"position":59,"content":"So what would you say you were most satisfied with today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/59.mp3","time_start":155.45,"time_end":158.92},{"position":60,"content":"Well, I like the wifi on the train.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-4-part-1-2023-01-19-23-41-09/60.mp3","time_start":159.19,"time_end":162.47},{"position":61,"content":"It's improved a lot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictati